\">Social Tools</a></div><div class=\"hidden items-center gap-3 lg:flex\"><button type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Switch to light theme\" title=\"Switch to light theme\" class=\"inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/15 bg-slate-900 text-xs font-bold\">SUN</button><a class=\"rounded-full bg-blue-600 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-blue-950/30 transition hover:bg-blue-500\" href=\"/request-tool\">Request New Tool</a></div><button type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Toggle navigation menu\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"inline-flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-slate-900 text-white lg:hidden\"><span class=\"flex w-5 flex-col gap-1.5\"><span class=\"h-0.5 rounded-full bg-current\"></span><span class=\"h-0.5 rounded-full bg-current\"></span><span class=\"h-0.5 rounded-full bg-current\"></span></span></button></div></nav><section class=\"px-6 py-20\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-4xl\"><div class=\"mb-10 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-8\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase text-blue-300\">Last updated: June 17, 2026</p><h1 class=\"mb-4 text-5xl font-black tracking-tight\">Contact</h1><p class=\"max-w-3xl text-lg leading-8 text-slate-300\">Reach A2ZConvertor for tool support, privacy questions, feedback and launch issues.</p></div><div class=\"grid gap-5 text-slate-300\"><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/60 p-6\"><h2 class=\"mb-3 text-2xl font-bold text-white\">How to get help</h2><p class=\"leading-7\">Need help with A2ZConvertor, want to report an issue, or have a launch-related question? Send an email and include the tool name, browser, device and a short description of what happened.</p></section><section class=\"grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-5\"><p class=\"mb-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-400\">General questions</p><a href=\"mailto:info@a2zconvertor.co.uk\" class=\"text-lg font-bold text-blue-300 hover:text-blue-200\">info@a2zconvertor.co.uk</a></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-5\"><p class=\"mb-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-400\">Contact and partnerships</p><a href=\"mailto:contact@a2zconvertor.co.uk\" class=\"text-lg font-bold text-blue-300 hover:text-blue-200\">contact@a2zconvertor.co.uk</a></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-5\"><p class=\"mb-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-400\">Tool support</p><a href=\"mailto:support@a2zconvertor.co.uk\" class=\"text-lg font-bold text-blue-300 hover:text-blue-200\">support@a2zconvertor.co.uk</a></div></section><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/60 p-6\"><h2 class=\"mb-3 text-2xl font-bold text-white\">Browser-based tools</h2><p class=\"leading-7\">A2ZConvertor does not require accounts. Many file tools run in your browser, so avoid attaching sensitive files unless support specifically asks for a sample you are comfortable sharing.</p></section></div></div></section><footer class=\"border-t border-white/10 px-6 py-16\"><div class=\"mx-auto mb-12 max-w-7xl\"><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-5\"><div class=\"\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-black\">Get new free tools and productivity tips.</h2><p class=\"mt-3 max-w-2xl leading-7 text-slate-400\">Be first to know when we launch new converters, PDF tools and browser-based productivity tools.</p><form class=\"mt-5 flex gap-3 flex-col\"><label class=\"sr-only\" for=\"_R_tbsnlb_\">Email address</label><input id=\"_R_tbsnlb_\" type=\"email\" required=\"\" autoComplete=\"email\" placeholder=\"you@example.com\" class=\"min-w-0 flex-1 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950 px-4 py-3 text-white outline-none focus:border-blue-500\" name=\"email\" value=\"\"/><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"source\" value=\"a2zconvertor\"/><button type=\"submit\" class=\"rounded-xl bg-blue-600 px-5 py-3 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-500\">Join by email</button></form><p class=\"mt-3 text-xs leading-5 text-slate-500\">No newsletter provider is connected yet. This opens your email app; we do not fake a stored subscription.</p></div></section></div><div class=\"mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-10 md:grid-cols-4\"><div><h3 class=\"mb-4 text-2xl font-black\">A2Z<span class=\"text-blue-500\">Convertor</span></h3><p class=\"text-slate-400\">Free online tools to convert, compress and edit files quickly.</p></div><div><h4 class=\"mb-4 font-bold\">Categories</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-slate-400\"><li><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" href=\"/tools\">All Tools</a></li><li><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" href=\"/image-tools\">Image Tools</a></li><li><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" href=\"/pdf-tools\">PDF Tools</a></li><li><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" href=\"/video-tools\">Video Tools</a></li><li><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" href=\"/audio-tools\">Audio Tools</a></li><li><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" href=\"/text-tools\">Text Tools</a></li><li><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" href=\"/social-media-tools\">Social Media Tools</a></li></ul></div><div><h4 class=\"mb-4 font-bold\">Popular Tools</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-slate-400\"><li><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" href=\"/convert/jpg-to-png\">JPG to PNG</a></li><li><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" href=\"/convert/compress-image\">Compress Image</a></li><li><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" href=\"/convert/pdf-merge\">PDF Merge</a></li><li><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" href=\"/convert/compress-pdf\">Compress PDF</a></li></ul></div><div><h4 class=\"mb-4 font-bold\">Company</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-slate-400\"><li><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" href=\"/ai-tools\">AI Tools</a></li><li><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" href=\"/support\">Support Us</a></li><li><a class=\"transiti